{{!
  CHARGEN CUSTOM CONTENT SNIPPET

  Adds the Secret and Goal form fields to the chargen process.

  FILE: ares-webportal/app/templates/components/chargen-custom.hbs

  STEP 1: Locate the file
  1. Open your game's ares-webportal/app/templates/components/chargen-custom.hbs

  STEP 2: Find the insertion point
  2. Find the <div class="tab-content"> element
  3. Look for the closing </div> tag for that tab-content div
  4. The new tab-pane should go INSIDE the tab-content, right before the </div>

  STEP 3: Copy and paste
  5. Copy the entire <div class="tab-pane"> block below (between the markers)
  6. Paste it inside the tab-content div at the end (before </div>)
  7. Save the file

  IMPORTANT DETAILS:

  ID MATCHING:
  - The id="chargen-inklings-pane" below MUST match the href in chargen-custom-tabs.snippet.hbs
  - Do NOT change this value

  FORM FIELDS:
  - This creates 4 fields: secret title, secret text, goal title, goal text
  - These correspond to the field names in chargen-custom.snippet.js
  - If you prefer rich text editing, swap the <textarea> elements for a markdown editor

  FIELD NAMES:
  - inkling_secret_title, inkling_secret_text, inkling_goal_title, inkling_goal_text
  - These names MUST match exactly what chargen-custom.snippet.js sends
}}

{{! ---START COPY HERE--- }}
<div class="tab-pane fade" id="chargen-inklings-pane">
  <div class="form-group">
    <label for="chargen-secret-title">Secret - Title</label>
    {{input id="chargen-secret-title" type="text" value=this.char.custom.inkling_secret_title placeholder="A short title for your secret"}}
  </div>
  <div class="form-group">
    <label for="chargen-secret-text">Secret - Description</label>
    {{textarea id="chargen-secret-text" value=this.char.custom.inkling_secret_text placeholder="Describe an IC secret your character holds..." rows=4}}
  </div>

  <div class="form-group">
    <label for="chargen-goal-title">Goal - Title</label>
    {{input id="chargen-goal-title" type="text" value=this.char.custom.inkling_goal_title placeholder="A short title for your goal"}}
  </div>
  <div class="form-group">
    <label for="chargen-goal-text">Goal - Description</label>
    {{textarea id="chargen-goal-text" value=this.char.custom.inkling_goal_text placeholder="Describe what your character is working toward..." rows=4}}
  </div>
</div>
{{! ---END COPY--- }}
